Detailed Description

Structure for meta information about the item data retrieved from the data store. Corresponds to the MetInf element type in the SyncML Meta-Information DTD.

Field Documentation

String SyncMLItemMetaInfo::m_format
 

Specifies the encoding format of the content information in the data element. Corresponds to the Format element in the SyncML Meta-Information DTD. Has to be one of bin, bool, b64, chr, int, node, null or xml. Mandatory!

String SyncMLItemMetaInfo::m_mark
 

Specifies a meta-information "mark" on the data object. Should be draft, final, delete, undelete, read, unread, etc. Corresponds to the Mark element in the SyncML Meta-Information DTD. Optional!

UINT32 SyncMLItemMetaInfo::m_size
 

Specifies the byte size of a data object. Corresponds to the Size element in the SyncML Meta-Information DTD. Optional!

String SyncMLItemMetaInfo::m_type
 

Specifies the media type of the content information in the Data element. Corresponds to the Type element in the SyncML Meta-Information DTD. Mandatory!

String SyncMLItemMetaInfo::m_version
 

Specifies the version identifier of a data object. Corresponds to the Version element in the SyncML Meta-Information DTD. Optional!
